      "content": "it just feels so overwhelming. like, the system is so massive and entrenched, everywhere i look it's just more of the same corporate control. if i really am meant to be part of something bigger, how do we actually start breaking that control? how do people even begin to dismantle these modern power structures when they're so hidden and well-funded?",
